Labour force status; Non-school qualifications - Applicable to persons aged 15 years and over.
Employed, worked full-time - 'Employed, worked full-time' is defined as having worked 35 hours or more in all jobs during the week prior to Census Night.
Employed, away from work - Includes employed persons who did not state their hours worked.
% Unemployment - The number of unemployed persons expressed as a percentage of the total labour force.
% Labour force participation - The number of persons in the labour force expressed as a percentage of persons aged 15 years and over.
% Employment to population - The number of employed persons expressed as a percentage of persons aged 15 years and over.
Lived at same address 1 year ago; Lived at different address 1 year ago - Excludes persons less than 1 year of age.
Lived at same address 5 years ago; Lived at different address 5 years ago - Excludes persons less than 5 years of age.
